snippet.title: TwinBee Portable
snippet.description:
One of Konami's game compilations for the PlayStation Portable, including the original TwinBee, Detana!! TwinBee, TwinBee Yahho!, Pop'n TwinBee, and a remake of TwinBee Da!! including a few extras.

Pop'n TwinBee was not played in this video due to its length and how good I am at it, but you may check my gameplay video of it on my channel.

Now if only those games had support for 2 players, especially TwinBee Da!!...

Final scores:
TwinBee - 413,500
Detana!! TwinBee - 90,050
TwinBee Yahho! - 437,550
TwinBee Da!! - 941,950
